{
  "$schema": "./brand.schema.json",
  "name": "White Label",
  "description": "Default white-label theme. Fork this file per brand, then run `npm run brand:build`. Neutral base values are the exact OKLCH of the shadcn-skills-design-starter (Design with AI) so AI-generated components interop 1:1 BRAND: primary is the teal action shade (brand.primary.600 #217D80) — NOT the 300 tint (#60CFCB), which carries white text at 1.86:1. primary-hover is 700 (#1F6366): the hover DARKENS instead of fading, because hover:bg-primary/80 mixes the fill toward the page and drops white text to 3.38:1.",
